{
  "stem": "7781.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't sleep, and so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went to there, and it was-- she suffered a lot, my wife.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I could've taken it, but she was pregnant, and there was so noisy place, they were terrible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had a cousin, and I figured, you don't come to me, I'll go to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no pride.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No-- you know, necessity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We took a taxi, and the taxi ask me whether-- he found out, through the telephone book.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said give me a name, I'll find out where he lives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, you had plenty of Jewish people in New York that could speak Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he tells me, he said, I found it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She lives in the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, but it will cost you $4.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you have $4?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I'll give you $4.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He took us to the cousin that we-- this is the only cousin I knew from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, two.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we went there, and we surprised them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed there one night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next night, she put us on the subway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She sent us back to the HIAS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Came back to HIAS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew we weren't there, so we explained to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they put my wife in one room for other women, and I slept in the attic, you know, with the men.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and slowly, you know, they took care of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They tried their best to take care of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and they sent me to Park Row.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I guess it was 15 Park Row in New York, where they took care on all the-- the-- the HIAS took care of all the-- they joined to care-- and the needs of the refugees.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got there, and there was a-- a social worker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
